headline: CSX (CSX): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q2 Earnings?
summary: CSX has followed the market’s trajectory closely, rising in tandem with the S&P 500 over the past six months. The stock has climbed by 13.2% to $33.85 per share while the index has gained 15.7%.
